A bus driver in critical condition and 29 others sustained injuries after a truck and an Intercape bus collided on N3 North near Voslooruson Sunday.The bus driver was airlifted to hospital after being trapped inside the vehicle. Jaws of life were to be used.29 other patients were transported to a nearby hospitals for further treatment.Motorists have advised to make use of the R103 as an alternative route.The cause of the incident is still unknown.-TNA Reporter